{"title":"Notion折腾--Mermaid图表工具","date":"2024-04-12T00:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Apr 12, 2024","L":"04/12/2024","MM-DD":"04-12"},"link":"2024/04/12/Notion折腾--Mermaid图表工具","updated":"2024-08-19T09:04:13.740Z","content":"<h1 id=\"简介\">简介<a title=\"#简介\" href=\"#简介\"></a></h1>\n<p>先简单介绍下Mermaid：</p>\n<p>Mermaid是一个基于JavaScript语法的制图工具，可以理解为你输入代码，Mermaid为你生成图表，包括且不限于：流程图、思维导图、甘特图、关系图、饼图、象限图等等，具体可参见Mermaid官方文档：<a href=\"https://mermaid.js.org/intro/\" target=\"_blank\">https://mermaid.js.org/intro/</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mermaid.js.org/intro/\" target=\"_blank\">https://mermaid.js.org/intro/</a></p>\n<p>熟悉Markdown格式的朋友都知道，Markdown快捷、简便，并且支持嵌入多种语言代码和图片、超链接等，因此以Markdown为主力格式写笔记非常方便，尤其是对于需要coding的小伙伴。但是有的时候在工作中想要记录一些关系图思维导图等，很多笔记软件就难以兼容，不得不另起软件，非常麻烦，于是Mermaid就应运而生了。<br>\n那么废话不多说，我们直入主题。</p>\n<h1 id=\"mermaid-展示\"><strong>Mermaid 展示</strong><a title=\"#mermaid-展示\" href=\"#mermaid-展示\"></a></h1>\n<p>我们以Notion为例，首先在笔记中开启一个代码框，直接输入Mermaid代码：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">flowchart TD</span><br><span class=\"line\">    A[上班] --&gt;|当牛马| B(有钱)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    B --&gt; C&#123;成为人上人&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    C --&gt;|One| D[开路虎]</span><br><span class=\"line\">    C --&gt;|Two| E[买豪宅]</span><br><span class=\"line\">    C --&gt;|Three| F[走上人生巅峰]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>我们就获得了这样一个流程图：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">flowchart TD</span><br><span class=\"line\">    A[上班] --&gt;|当牛马| B(有钱)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    B --&gt; C&#123;成为人上人&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    C --&gt;|One| D[开路虎]</span><br><span class=\"line\">    C --&gt;|Two| E[买豪宅]</span><br><span class=\"line\">    C --&gt;|Three| F[走上人生巅峰]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>Notion支持代码和图表共同显示，展示出来，就是这样的：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Lq0ne/my_pic/202408191536987.png\" alt=\"image.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>不仅如此，你甚至可以将其当作绘图工具（妈妈再也不用担心我画不出拓扑图辣）：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">graph TD</span><br><span class=\"line\">%% 网络拓扑图</span><br><span class=\"line\"> linkStyle default interpolate basis</span><br><span class=\"line\"> wan1[&lt;center&gt;DSL 100/10 Mb&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;10.100.102.1&lt;/center&gt;]---router&#123;&lt;center&gt;核心交换机&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;10.20.30.1&lt;/center&gt;&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"> ip((&lt;center&gt;&lt;br&gt;IP&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/center&gt;))-.-router</span><br><span class=\"line\"> dns((&lt;center&gt;&lt;br&gt;DNS&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/center&gt;))-.-router</span><br><span class=\"line\"> wan2[&lt;center&gt;测试区&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;192.168.1.1&lt;/center&gt;]---router</span><br><span class=\"line\"> router---|100Mb|ap[&lt;center&gt;生产区&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;10.20.30.3&lt;/center&gt;]</span><br><span class=\"line\"> router---|1Gb|pc(&lt;center&gt;办公区&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;10.20.30.190&lt;/center&gt;)</span><br><span class=\"line\"> router---|1Gb|switch[&lt;center&gt;核心数据库&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;10.20.30.2&lt;/center&gt;]</span><br><span class=\"line\"> subgraph red1</span><br><span class=\"line\"> ap-.-cam1(&lt;center&gt;Camera&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;10.20.30.171&lt;/center&gt;)</span><br><span class=\"line\"> ap-.-cam2(&lt;center&gt;Camera&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;10.20.30.172&lt;/center&gt;)</span><br><span class=\"line\"> ap-.-phone(&lt;center&gt;Phone&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;10.20.30.191&lt;/center&gt;)</span><br><span class=\"line\"> ap-.-ir(&lt;center&gt;IR&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;10.20.30.180&lt;/center&gt;)</span><br><span class=\"line\"> end</span><br><span class=\"line\"> subgraph red2</span><br><span class=\"line\"> switch---|100Mb|pi1(&lt;center&gt;RPi 3B&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;10.20.30.150&lt;/center&gt;)</span><br><span class=\"line\"> switch---|1Gb|pi2(&lt;center&gt;RPi 3B+&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;10.20.30.151&lt;/center&gt;)</span><br><span class=\"line\"> switch---|100Mb|nvr(&lt;center&gt;NVR&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;10.20.30.170&lt;/center&gt;)</span><br><span class=\"line\"> switch---|1Gb|laptop(&lt;center&gt;Laptop&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;10.20.30.192&lt;/center&gt;)</span><br><span class=\"line\"> end</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">gitGraph</span><br><span class=\"line\">%% git</span><br><span class=\"line\">   commit</span><br><span class=\"line\">   commit</span><br><span class=\"line\">   branch develop</span><br><span class=\"line\">   commit</span><br><span class=\"line\">   commit</span><br><span class=\"line\">   commit</span><br><span class=\"line\">   checkout main</span><br><span class=\"line\">   commit</span><br><span class=\"line\">   commit</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>无需使用鼠标不优雅的点来点去，也不用开一个新的思维导图软件，更不用将思维导图截图嵌入，而是直接渲染生成，极为的方便优雅快捷。</p>\n<h1 id=\"参考：\">参考：<a title=\"#参考：\" href=\"#参考：\"></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://mermaid.js.org/intro/\" target=\"_blank\">https://mermaid.js.org/intro/</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://cloud.tencent.com/developer/article/2347512\" target=\"_blank\">https://cloud.tencent.com/developer/article/2347512</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n","prev":{"title":"[PG Play]--Monitoring","link":"2024/07/10/[PG Play]--Monitoring"},"next":{"title":"渗透测试杂谈--权限范围与权限级别","link":"2023/09/13/渗透测试杂谈--权限范围与权限级别"},"plink":"https://Lq0ne.github.io/2024/04/12/Notion折腾--Mermaid图表工具/","toc":[{"id":"简介","title":"简介","index":"1"},{"id":"mermaid-展示","title":"Mermaid 展示","index":"2"},{"id":"参考：","title":"参考：","index":"3"}],"copyright":{"license":"个人原创 - 自由转载 - 保持署名 - 禁止商用","published":"April 12, 2024","author":"Lq0ne","link":"<a href=\"https://Lq0ne.github.io/2024/04/12/Notion折腾--Mermaid图表工具/\" title=\"Notion折腾--Mermaid图表工具\">https://Lq0ne.github.io/2024/04/12/Notion折腾--Mermaid图表工具/</a>"},"reading_time":"742 words in 5 min"}